Maaf!  Maaf!  - Saaransh!

00:13:38.880 --> 00:13:40.880
Saya sangat minta maaf!  - Ayo!

00:13:52.920 --> 00:13:55.480
Ayah, sepertinya Pak
Armaan ada di sini!

